Package: sinodate
Title: S4 class to represent date in Chinese calendar (Mandarin: Nongli, Cantonese: Nung Lik)
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: "Chung-hong Chan <Chung-hong Chan> [aut, cre]"
Description: S4 class to represent date in Chinese calendar. Also provided functions for conversion between Gregorian date and sinodate.
Depends: R (>= 3.0.0)
Imports: lubridate
License: MIT
LazyData: true
